sequenceDiagram
    %% {{REPLACE_WITH_TRACE_EVIDENCE}}
    participant Actor
    participant Controller
    participant Service
    participant Adapter

    Actor->>Controller: Trigger
    Controller->>Service: Execute
    alt MAIN
        Service->>Adapter: Apply side effect
        Adapter-->>Service: Result
        Service-->>Actor: Outcome
    else ERROR
        Service-->>Actor: Error/recovery outcome
    end
